<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Show Page</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1><%= films.title%></h1>
    <p><%= films.director%> directed this film.</p>
    <p> The film was made in <%= films.country%>. </p>
    <p> Premise: <%= films.plot%> </p>
    <p> The genre of the film can be classified as <%= films.genre%>.  </p>
    <p> The film takes place in <%= films.setting%>. </p>
    <p> The run time of the film is <%= films.runTime%>  minutes. </p>
    <p> The language primarily spoken by actors in the film is <%= films.languages%>.  </p>
    <% if (films.seenTheFilm) {%>
        <p> I have seen this film!</p>
    <% } else {%>
        <p> I have NOT seen this film!</p>
    <% } %>
    <img width="250" src="<%= films.filmPoster%>"/> 
     <br/>
    <a href="/films">Back to Index</a>
</body>
</html>
